---
const pathname = new URL(Astro.request.url).pathname;
---

<h1>Thunderbird QR生成</h1>

<nav class="nav-links">
    <a href="/" class={pathname === "/" ? "active" : ""}>作成フォーム</a>
    <a href="/bulk" class={pathname === "/bulk" ? "active" : ""}>一括読み込み</a
    >
    <a href="/guide" class={pathname === "/guide" ? "active" : ""}
        >仕様・使い方解説</a
    >
</nav>

<p class="description">
    設定情報を入力し、ボタンを押すと<br />別タブで設定用QRコードが表示されます。
</p>

<style>
    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #666;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition:
            background-color 0.2s,
            color 0.2s;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        color: #333;
    }

    .nav-links a.active {
        background-color: #e7f1ff;
        color: #007bff;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .description {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 2em;
    }
</style>
